      "updated": 1758743912352,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 19.567856197291373,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "Encapsulation: \nBundles the data and methods into single unit(class) \nand restrict access to some of the object's component to \nprotect the internal state",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Encapsulation: \nBundles the data and methods into single unit(class) \nand restrict access to some of the object's component to \nprotect the internal state",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "version": 728,
      "versionNonce": 1015232397,
      "index": "aD",
      "isDeleted": false,
      "id": "fGeIHw7pH_TAQDXEZ295C",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "x": 436.6998136758475,
      "y": -192.66830625094008,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#a5d8ff",
      "width": 561.1596069335938,
      "height": 75,
      "seed": 1874466435,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1755262432224,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "Inheritance:\nAllows one class (subclass) to inherit the properties and \nmethods from the another class (parent class)",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Inheritance:\nAllows one class (subclass) to inherit the properties and \nmethods from the another class (parent class)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "version": 720,
      "versionNonce": 706188227,
      "index": "aE",
      "isDeleted": false,
      "id": "ja02p7lEL35Bf-saiouYB",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "x": 431.1239649969857,
      "y": -75.53439151832572,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#a5d8ff",
      "width": 575.1796264648438,
      "height": 75,
      "seed": 1843023395,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1755262432224,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "Abstraction:\nHides the complex implementation details and exposes only \nessential features",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Abstraction:\nHides the complex implementation details and exposes only \nessential features",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "version": 724,
      "versionNonce": 1438322259,
      "index": "aF",
      "isDeleted": false,
      "id": "sBq-TjEEnL9iqLJ5linrb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "x": 423.9708982405391,
      "y": 47.22104289604613,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#a5d8ff",
      "width": 594.1796875,
      "height": 75,
      "seed": 374510019,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1760054918692,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": " Polymorphism:\n Allows methods to do different things based on the object \n it is acting upon, supporting dynamic method resolution",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": " Polymorphism:\n Allows methods to do different things based on the object \n it is acting upon, supporting dynamic method resolution",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "version": 666,
      "versionNonce": 303440739,
      "index": "aG",
      "isDeleted": false,
      "id": "3pL-P_ShFzK7zU8I1EcvE",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "x": 1297.8286218243456,
      "y": -326.45151295240794,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffc9c9",
      "width": 523.799560546875,
      "height": 75,
      "seed": 2051105123,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1755262432224,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "Association: (uses-a)\nwhere one class uses or interacts with another class \nor there is a logical relation b/w them ",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Association: (uses-a)\nwhere one class uses or interacts with another class \nor there is a logical relation b/w them ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "version": 723,
      "versionNonce": 1549432909,
      "index": "aH",
      "isDeleted": false,
      "id": "ghkLDihMVJvGn_m45g7Ut",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "x": 1297.9540803015307,
      "y": -218.97548373951577,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffc9c9",
      "width": 651.7995361685753,
      "height": 100,
      "seed": 49626371,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1755262432224,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "Aggregation: (has-a)\nwhere one class(the whole) contains another class(the part), given\nthat the part can exist independently \nEx: Car and Engine",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Aggregation: (has-a)\nwhere one class(the whole) contains another class(the part), given\nthat the part can exist independently \nEx: Car and Engine",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "version": 636,
      "versionNonce": 115457795,
      "index": "aI",
      "isDeleted": false,
      "id": "D6laCdufUCIOJplHLq2R_",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "x": 1298.5114708311712,
      "y": -85.09694814945397,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffc9c9",
      "width": 659.759521484375,
      "height": 100,
      "seed": 1810670755,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1755262432224,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "Composition: (strong has-a)\nwhere one class(the whole) contains another class(the part), given \nthat the part can't exist independently \nEx: House and Room",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Composition: (strong has-a)\nwhere one class(the whole) contains another class(the part), given \nthat the part can't exist independently \nEx: House and Room",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
