      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1755262432224,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "When we can create different type of objects based on the client preference, We want to \nadd that logic into a factory class that takes care of the creation. So creation is \ndone via interfaces rather than objects, etc.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "When we can create different type of objects based on the client preference, We want to \nadd that logic into a factory class that takes care of the creation. So creation is \ndone via interfaces rather than objects, etc.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
